$values.Text: This sequence runs continuously 24/7. It is safe to start any time of day.
Primary goals for this sequence:
1. Keep the scope safe - park whenever not imaging the sky
2. Run without user intervention continuously
3. Get flats and darks whenever requested without interrupting the sequence
4. Keep the team informed about sequence progress via Discord
5. Run continuously or in single night mode
Autonomous v0.4.0 started
There are two global constants that need to be set for this sequence to work: THIS_OBSERVATORY and RUN_CONTINUOUSLY.
Set THIS_OBSERVATORY to the integer valu that corresponds to your observatory (from down below (e.g. 2 for DSOC_CERAVOLO).
Set RUN_CONTINUOUSLY to 1 to run 24/7 without interruption or 0 to run one night and then exit.
